{"tid":305880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黑色五毛警報]見到呢個post可以過千正評，證明連登仔又被五毛擺佈","createTime":"2017-07-02T05:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T23:01:39.000Z","uid":81113,"like":63,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df844cec769cc9ab543398f08bd7dd1b10d77dd2","tid":305880,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"Topic未必出得曬: [黑色五毛警報]見到呢個post可以過千正評，證明連登仔又被五毛擺佈<br />\n<br />\n今時今日班臭雞仲要求搞婚禮真係好不知廉恥<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/305091/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/305091/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n首先呢個topic絕對唔係時事<br />\n但又放時事台，仲咁啱71先出<br />\n再起下開post條撚樣個底<br />\n名就叫台灣獨立<br />\n實際就推香港人做中國人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/130837_8a45c2371acbc5d085d1f6d470bf886c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F130837_8a45c2371acbc5d085d1f6d470bf886c.jpg&h=ecd01cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/130838_26cc11796c2acb18bd2880825b6c1b4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F130838_26cc11796c2acb18bd2880825b6c1b4b.jpg&h=3169c5d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過千名連登仔被五毛呃like，想笑死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有呀,佢個 post第一句「唔識個羞字點寫」<br />\n<br />\n條五毛連個醜字都唔識寫架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/134235_75e7be489bb44c505c63bcbba46ceef2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F134235_75e7be489bb44c505c63bcbba46ceef2.jpg&h=a685ed01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地話連登仔低質<br />\n<br />\n其實我都想撐連登仔<br />\n<br />\n但係睇到呢度，比人撚，比人利用，一d批判／逆思維都冇<br />\n<br />\n我真係撐唔住<br />\n<br />\n你地繼續不思進取咁屌港女啦<br />\n<br />\n屌得多就會有女架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n引用資料:<br />\n<br />\n真係好多五毛惡意挑撥香港男女問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/299614/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/299614/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74bc1d422e502496817d071da21376a72908d437","tid":305880,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:52:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f465cf4fbce569b244833175973a2f3fbfd99df","tid":305880,"uid":81113,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又捉到5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880a8e3b62b60961621bf4773fc0ac860bd332e7","tid":305880,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:58:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff881bb6abd91a2ae41f6d3a04e1949fc15c1e99","tid":305880,"uid":37030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:03:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55de5e0e8968158375685611f81708679ee4d252","tid":305880,"uid":28800,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:10:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d78bec9200ea30292a64bd174c2d39b219ad189f","tid":305880,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51ddf9f77b993638de9004c01487046a088a5af5","tid":305880,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:57:56.000Z","msg":"留意左呢條友一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3856b8ac937349bc2f747707735d3644e153171","tid":305880,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:02:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98b7993dd87d3e7631ff371091382838511c5758","tid":305880,"uid"